                                    ::Razael::

    After a long, venturous=
 run, Razael switched back to robot mode after the cunning femme bot found =
what she was looking for.  That being, the base that her scanners had notif=
ied her of.  Razael kept a distance and took cover by the nearest tree, in =
case defenses opened fire, or if transformers in the base attacked her.  Sh=
e sent a transmission to the base(the Maximal base).

    "If you are recie=
ving this message," she said, "I come in peace and would like to negotiate =
an alliance."

    Razael cautiously stayed by her cover, and waited for a =
reply from someone.
